title: Class - Outdoor-Wall lamps
description: Timeless, elegant and enduring, the Class wall lamp evokes a sense of nostalgia. Its translucent glass tube is fluted, defined by even grooves that allow the light to pass softly through it while the source remains obscured. Each Class outdoor lampâ€™s tube is supported by a robust aluminium shaft, its matte black contrasting with the smooth surface of the glass tubes, resulting in a satisfying combination of textures reminiscent of the traditional gas lamp.
